snippet.title: Evercade Bitmap Brothers Collection 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
More Information - https://www.evercade.co.uk/cartridges/bitmap-brothers-collection-1

The Bitmap Brothers Collection 1 cartridge brings 5 classic games from the British "rock star" developers to the Evercade, including: The Chaos Engine, Xenon 2: Megablast, Speedball and more!

Games List:

- The Chaos Engine
- Speedball
- Speedball 2: Brutal Deluxe
- Speedball 2100
- Xenon 2: Megablast
